overview.longBusinessSummary: Kyndryl Holdings, Inc. operates as a technology services company and IT infrastructure services provider in the United States, Japan, and internationally. The company offers cloud services; core enterprise and zCloud services; application, data, and artificial intelligence services; digital workplace services; security and resiliency services; and network services and edge services. It serves financial, healthcare, public, technology, media and telecom, retail, travel, and automotive industries. Kyndryl Holdings, Inc. was incorporated in 2020 and is headquartered in New York, New York.
